Quick numeric breakdown (e.g. Seed 1.5/2, Pivot 2/2 … total 8.5/10).

Two-line overall summary (strength + key area to improve).

One actionable next step (e.g. “try to articulate pitfalls explicitly even if trivial”).

This way, every commentary you produce gets a quantitative benchmark plus one sharp improvement hook — steady progress, drill by drill.

