Value = (Dream Outcome × Perceived Likelihood of Achievement) ÷ (Time Delay × Effort & Sacrifice). Increase the top (bigger dream, more certainty) and shrink the bottom (faster results, less effort). Hormozi treats this as the literal formula to engineer offers and messaging. 

