4) Optimize unit economics before scaling.

Know your CPA → payback period → gross margin → LTV. Don’t scale a leaky funnel. Gym Launch and his early playbook emphasize perfecting one reliable acquisition channel and the economics behind it. 

Do this now: calculate: Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC), Average Purchase Value, Gross Margin %, and payback period. If payback > acceptable horizon, fix funnel before spending to scale.


