6) Stack guarantees and remove risk to boost perceived likelihood.

Refunds, results guarantees, and escalated support are cheap perception multipliers that increase willingness to buy. Hormozi emphasizes certainty as what people actually pay for. 

Do this now: add a “results or refund” clause or a staged guarantee with clear metrics.


---

7) Make value immediate and effortless (attack the denominator of the Value Equation).

Deliver quick wins, done-for-you components, or concierge onboarding to reduce effort & time. The biggest leverage is reducing time and effort. 

