Risk: Drift in tone / pedagogy across 1,000 commentaries.
Mitigation: strict editorial rubric; automated checks for metadata; periodic style audits.

Risk: Over-formalization reduces accessibility.
Mitigation: maintain MVC stage as conversational filter; require Stage-1 acceptance.

